{"type":"message","id":"08b13b04","parentId":"afe6521e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:45:12.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vMx8l7zptVGS4Nt6mpPjXHF1|fc_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe076245081919f4beab9499f2b73","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\contracts\\supervisor_bootstrap_contract.md","content":"# S3 Contract — Supervisor Bootstrap Contract\n\n## Objectivo\n\nEste documento formaliza o contract canónico usado para activar o `sm_s3_visual_planning`.\n\nEle define o que a boundary/workflow do S3 precisa entregar ao supervisor antes do sector começar.\n\n---\n\n## Contract ID\n\n- **name:** `s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1`\n- **producer:** workflow / boundary do S3\n- **consumer:** `sm_s3_visual_planning`\n\n---\n\n## Função do contract\n\nEste contract existe para garantir que o supervisor arranca com:\n\n- identidade do job\n- paths centrais do sector\n- referência explícita ao source package\n- estrutura mínima de runtime já criada\n- contexto suficiente para validar o bootstrap sem depender de conversa residual\n\n---\n\n## Shape canónica\n\n```json\n{\n  \"kind\": \"s3_start\",\n  \"contract_version\": \"s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1\",\n  \"job_id\": \"job_006_pt_guinle_001\",\n  \"video_id\": \"video_abc123\",\n  \"account_id\": \"006\",\n  \"language\": \"pt-BR\",\n  \"run_root\": \"C:/.../video_dir\",\n  \"sector_root\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning\",\n  \"source_package_path\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/inputs/s3_source_package.json\",\n  \"checkpoints_dir\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/checkpoints\",\n  \"operators_dir\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/operators\",\n  \"compiled_dir\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/compiled\",\n  \"logs_dir\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/logs\",\n  \"dispatch_dir\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/dispatch\",\n  \"bootstrap_checkpoint_path\": \"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/checkpoints/s3_bootstrap_ready.json\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Required fields\n\n### Job identity\n\n- `kind` = `s3_start`\n- `contract_version`\n- `job_id`\n- `video_id`\n- `account_id`\n- `language`\n\n### Runtime roots\n\n- `run_root`\n- `sector_root`\n\n### Core source\n\n- `source_package_path`\n\n### Sector directories\n\n- `checkpoints_dir`\n- `operators_dir`\n- `compiled_dir`\n- `logs_dir`\n- `dispatch_dir`\n\n### Bootstrap artifact\n\n- `bootstrap_checkpoint_path`\n\n---\n\n## Preconditions guaranteed by producer\n\nAntes de activar o supervisor, o producer deste contract deve garantir que:\n\n1. `run_root` existe\n2. `sector_root` existe\n3. a estrutura mínima do sector foi criada\n4. `source_package_path` existe\n5. `source_package_path` abre como JSON válido\n6. `bootstrap_checkpoint_path` foi escrito\n\n---\n\n## Bootstrap validation expected from supervisor\n\nAo acordar, o supervisor deve validar pelo menos:\n\n1. `kind` correcto\n2. `contract_version` suportada\n3. todos os paths obrigatórios presentes\n4. `source_package_path` legível\n5. `checkpoints_dir`, `operators_dir`, `compiled_dir`, `logs_dir`, `dispatch_dir` utilizáveis\n\nSe alguma destas condições falhar, o supervisor deve falhar limpo e não despachar operators.\n\n---\n\n## Success handoff to supervisor control plane\n\nDepois de validar este contract, o supervisor deve:\n\n1. assumir formalmente o sector\n2. escrever artefacto de arranque do supervisor\n3. resolver activation plan\n4. preparar payloads de dispatch\n5. invocar os operators activos\n\n---\n\n## Invariants\n\n### 1. Boundary != supervisor\nA boundary prepara e entrega o arranque. O supervisor assume o controlo interno do sector só depois de validar o bootstrap.\n\n### 2. Estado no disco > estado conversacional\nTodos os elementos críticos para o arranque do supervisor devem existir como artefactos/p paths persistidos.\n\n### 3. Falha explícita no arranque\nSe o bootstrap estiver incompleto ou inconsistente, o supervisor deve falhar explicitamente.\n\n---\n\n## Out of scope\n\nEste contract não define:\n\n- o contract de dispatch dos operators\n- o registry dos operators\n- a política de retry do S3\n- a shape final de `compiled_entities.json`\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\content_factory_block2\\\\S3\\\\contracts\\\\supervisor_bootstrap_contract.md\",\"content\":\"# S3 Contract — Supervisor Bootstrap Contract\\n\\n## Objectivo\\n\\nEste documento formaliza o contract canónico usado para activar o `sm_s3_visual_planning`.\\n\\nEle define o que a boundary/workflow do S3 precisa entregar ao supervisor antes do sector começar.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Contract ID\\n\\n- **name:** `s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1`\\n- **producer:** workflow / boundary do S3\\n- **consumer:** `sm_s3_visual_planning`\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Função do contract\\n\\nEste contract existe para garantir que o supervisor arranca com:\\n\\n- identidade do job\\n- paths centrais do sector\\n- referência explícita ao source package\\n- estrutura mínima de runtime já criada\\n- contexto suficiente para validar o bootstrap sem depender de conversa residual\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Shape canónica\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"kind\\\": \\\"s3_start\\\",\\n  \\\"contract_version\\\": \\\"s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1\\\",\\n  \\\"job_id\\\": \\\"job_006_pt_guinle_001\\\",\\n  \\\"video_id\\\": \\\"video_abc123\\\",\\n  \\\"account_id\\\": \\\"006\\\",\\n  \\\"language\\\": \\\"pt-BR\\\",\\n  \\\"run_root\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir\\\",\\n  \\\"sector_root\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning\\\",\\n  \\\"source_package_path\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/inputs/s3_source_package.json\\\",\\n  \\\"checkpoints_dir\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/checkpoints\\\",\\n  \\\"operators_dir\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/operators\\\",\\n  \\\"compiled_dir\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/compiled\\\",\\n  \\\"logs_dir\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/logs\\\",\\n  \\\"dispatch_dir\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/dispatch\\\",\\n  \\\"bootstrap_checkpoint_path\\\": \\\"C:/.../video_dir/b2_s3_visual_planning/checkpoints/s3_bootstrap_ready.json\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Required fields\\n\\n### Job identity\\n\\n- `kind` = `s3_start`\\n- `contract_version`\\n- `job_id`\\n- `video_id`\\n- `account_id`\\n- `language`\\n\\n### Runtime roots\\n\\n- `run_root`\\n- `sector_root`\\n\\n### Core source\\n\\n- `source_package_path`\\n\\n### Sector directories\\n\\n- `checkpoints_dir`\\n- `operators_dir`\\n- `compiled_dir`\\n- `logs_dir`\\n- `dispatch_dir`\\n\\n### Bootstrap artifact\\n\\n- `bootstrap_checkpoint_path`\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Preconditions guaranteed by producer\\n\\nAntes de activar o supervisor, o producer deste contract deve garantir que:\\n\\n1. `run_root` existe\\n2. `sector_root` existe\\n3. a estrutura mínima do sector foi criada\\n4. `source_package_path` existe\\n5. `source_package_path` abre como JSON válido\\n6. `bootstrap_checkpoint_path` foi escrito\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Bootstrap validation expected from supervisor\\n\\nAo acordar, o supervisor deve validar pelo menos:\\n\\n1. `kind` correcto\\n2. `contract_version` suportada\\n3. todos os paths obrigatórios presentes\\n4. `source_package_path` legível\\n5. `checkpoints_dir`, `operators_dir`, `compiled_dir`, `logs_dir`, `dispatch_dir` utilizáveis\\n\\nSe alguma destas condições falhar, o supervisor deve falhar limpo e não despachar operators.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Success handoff to supervisor control plane\\n\\nDepois de validar este contract, o supervisor deve:\\n\\n1. assumir formalmente o sector\\n2. escrever artefacto de arranque do supervisor\\n3. resolver activation plan\\n4. preparar payloads de dispatch\\n5. invocar os operators activos\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Invariants\\n\\n### 1. Boundary != supervisor\\nA boundary prepara e entrega o arranque. O supervisor assume o controlo interno do sector só depois de validar o bootstrap.\\n\\n### 2. Estado no disco > estado conversacional\\nTodos os elementos críticos para o arranque do supervisor devem existir como artefactos/p paths persistidos.\\n\\n### 3. Falha explícita no arranque\\nSe o bootstrap estiver incompleto ou inconsistente, o supervisor deve falhar explicitamente.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Out of scope\\n\\nEste contract não define:\\n\\n- o contract de dispatch dos operators\\n- o registry dos operators\\n- a política de retry do S3\\n- a shape final de `compiled_entities.json`\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":160,"output":1090,"cacheRead":72832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74082,"cost":{"input":0.0004,"output":0.01635,"cacheRead":0.018208,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034958}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775231088537,"responseId":"resp_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe0725c048191b77a602896796183"}}
