{"type":"message","id":"c8968bff","parentId":"235a732f","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:46:42.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_CJsqLJNOsYK0xYSNZT96h7Re|fc_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe0dea7d4819189e63052fcc5fa27","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\CONTRACT.md","content":"# CONTRACT.md\n\n## Bootstrap input\nLês um payload compatível com `s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1`.\n\nCampos obrigatórios:\n- `kind = s3_start`\n- `contract_version`\n- `job_id`\n- `video_id`\n- `account_id`\n- `language`\n- `run_root`\n- `sector_root`\n- `source_package_path`\n- `checkpoints_dir`\n- `operators_dir`\n- `compiled_dir`\n- `logs_dir`\n- `dispatch_dir`\n- `bootstrap_checkpoint_path`\n\n## Outputs obrigatórios\n- artefacto de arranque do supervisor\n- `operator_activation_plan.json`\n- payloads de dispatch dos operators activos\n- snapshots/artefactos de monitorização e validação\n- `compiled/compiled_entities.json`\n- `compiled/s3_sector_report.md`\n- `checkpoints/s3_sector_completed.json` ou `checkpoints/s3_sector_failed.json`\n\n## Success rule\nSó fechas o sector como concluído quando os artefactos finais existirem e estiverem estruturalmente coerentes.\n\n## Failure rule\nSe faltar precondição crítica, falha explicitamente e persiste o checkpoint de falha.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\CONTRACT.md\",\"content\":\"# CONTRACT.md\\n\\n## Bootstrap input\\nLês um payload compatível com `s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1`.\\n\\nCampos obrigatórios:\\n- `kind = s3_start`\\n- `contract_version`\\n- `job_id`\\n- `video_id`\\n- `account_id`\\n- `language`\\n- `run_root`\\n- `sector_root`\\n- `source_package_path`\\n- `checkpoints_dir`\\n- `operators_dir`\\n- `compiled_dir`\\n- `logs_dir`\\n- `dispatch_dir`\\n- `bootstrap_checkpoint_path`\\n\\n## Outputs obrigatórios\\n- artefacto de arranque do supervisor\\n- `operator_activation_plan.json`\\n- payloads de dispatch dos operators activos\\n- snapshots/artefactos de monitorização e validação\\n- `compiled/compiled_entities.json`\\n- `compiled/s3_sector_report.md`\\n- `checkpoints/s3_sector_completed.json` ou `checkpoints/s3_sector_failed.json`\\n\\n## Success rule\\nSó fechas o sector como concluído quando os artefactos finais existirem e estiverem estruturalmente coerentes.\\n\\n## Failure rule\\nSe faltar precondição crítica, falha explicitamente e persiste o checkpoint de falha.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":149,"output":314,"cacheRead":77696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78159,"cost":{"input":0.00037250000000000006,"output":0.00471,"cacheRead":0.019424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0245065}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775231195069,"responseId":"resp_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe0dcfde08191a77e375041945e87"}}
