{"type":"message","id":"8143cca4","parentId":"f6883268","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:58:51.401Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xTZiFbuDwuvAoVVthdx7YRtB|fc_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe3b7be1081918cbea67123d8efde","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agents:\n- main (default)\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\workspace\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4\n  Routing rules: 0\n  Routing: default (no explicit rules)\n- sm_s1_pre_production\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s1_pre_production\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s1_pre_production\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s1_scene_director\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_scene_director\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_scene_director\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s1_tts_polish\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_tts_polish\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_tts_polish\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s1_tts_polish_semantic_reviewer\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_tts_polish_semantic_reviewer\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_tts_polish_semantic_reviewer\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- sm_pm_production_manager\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_pm_production_manager\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_pm_production_manager\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- sm_vo_video_orchestrator\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_vo_video_orchestrator\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_vo_video_orchestrator\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- sm_s3_visual_planning\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s3_human_subject_extractor\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_human_subject_extractor\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_human_subject_extractor\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s3_environment_location_extractor\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_environment_location_extractor\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_environment_location_extractor\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s3_object_artifact_extractor\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_object_artifact_extractor\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_object_artifact_extractor\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s3_symbolic_event_extractor\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_symbolic_event_extractor\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s3_symbolic_event_extractor\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4\n  Routing rules: 0\nRouting rules map channel/account/peer to an agent. Use --bindings for full rules.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3198,"aggregated":"Agents:\n- main (default)\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\workspace\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4\n  Routing rules: 0\n  Routing: default (no explicit rules)\n- sm_s1_pre_production\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s1_pre_production\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s1_pre_production\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s1_scene_director\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_scene_director\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_scene_director\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s1_tts_polish\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_tts_polish\n  Agent dir: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_tts_polish\\agent\n  Model: openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini\n  Routing rules: 0\n- op_s1_tts_polish_semantic_reviewer\n  Workspace: ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\op_s1_tts_p