{"type":"message","id":"1adcb942","parentId":"3a8ef101","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:01:28.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Vou seguir o plano pela próxima etapa certa: alinhar os modelos dos agents para mini, depois materializar os helpers mínimos do S3 e preparar a ligação real B2 -> S3.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe4450f048191813204bb119c9ef2\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_IsxgVdvA0ukpQm1dNSr069LK|fc_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe446024c8191815366b2ede49847","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","edits":[{"oldText":"      {\n        \"id\": \"sm_s3_visual_planning\",\n        \"name\": \"sm_s3_visual_planning\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\agent\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"op_s3_human_subject_extractor\",\n        \"name\": \"op_s3_human_subject_extractor\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\op_s3_human_subject_extractor\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\op_s3_human_subject_extractor\\\\agent\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"op_s3_environment_location_extractor\",\n        \"name\": \"op_s3_environment_location_extractor\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\op_s3_environment_location_extractor\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\op_s3_environment_location_extractor\\\\agent\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"op_s3_object_artifact_extractor\",\n        \"name\": \"op_s3_object_artifact_extractor\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\op_s3_object_artifact_extractor\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\