{"type":"message","id":"61b13c67","parentId":"71a0b5a4","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:02:31.388Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yF3GmQCMa0moZY0oLw4W2DVk|fc_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe4890cf08191a1c5ea3eeb85775a","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_contracts.md","content":"# B2 — Minimal Runtime Contracts (v1)\n\n## Objectivo\n\nEste documento fecha a camada mínima de contracts operacionais do B2 necessária para ligar o `b2_director` ao S3 no primeiro teste S3-only.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Bootstrap contract do B2\n\n### Contract id\n- `b2.bootstrap.v1`\n\n### Shape mínima\n```json\n{\n  \"kind\": \"b2_start\",\n  \"contract_version\": \"b2.bootstrap.v1\",\n  \"job_id\": \"job_006_pt_001\",\n  \"run_root\": \"C:/.../run_root\",\n  \"b2_root\": \"C:/.../run_root/b2\",\n  \"account_id\": \"006\",\n  \"language\": \"pt-BR\",\n  \"inputs\": {\n    \"screenplay_analysis_path\": \"...\"\n  },\n  \"mode\": \"s3_only\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. Resume contract do B2 Director\n\n### Contract id\n- `b2.resume.v1`\n\n### Shape mínima\n```json\n{\n  \"kind\": \"b2_resume\",\n  \"contract_version\": \"b2.resume.v1\",\n  \"run_root\": \"C:/.../run_root\",\n  \"b2_root\": \"C:/.../run_root/b2\",\n  \"reason\": \"s3_completed\",\n  \"trigger_artifact\": \"C:/.../run_root/b2/checkpoints/s3_completed.json\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. Checkpoint de request do S3\n\nQuando o `b2_director` decide iniciar o S3, ele deve produzir:\n\n```text\n{b2_root}/checkpoints/s3_requested.json\n```\n\n### Shape mínima\n```json\n{\n  \"event\": \"s3_requested\",\n  \"job_id\": \"job_006_pt_001\",\n  \"sector\": \"s3_visual_planning\",\n  \"requested_at\": \"ISO_TIMESTAMP\",\n  \"supervisor_agent_id\": \"sm_s3_visual_planning\",\n  \"mode\": \"s3_only\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. Checkpoint de conclusão do S3\n\nQuando o S3 fechar com sucesso utilizável, o supervisor deve produzir:\n\n```text\n{b2_root}/checkpoints/s3_completed.json\n```\n\n### Shape mínima\n```json\n{\n  \"event\": \"s3_completed\",\n  \"job_id\": \"job_006_pt_001\",\n  \"sector\": \"s3_visual_planning\",\n  \"compiled_entities_path\": \"C:/.../compiled/compiled_entities.json\",\n  \"sector_report_path\": \"C:/.../compiled/s3_sector_report.md\",\n  \"completed_at\": \"ISO_TIMESTAMP\",\n  \"status\": \"completed\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Checkpoint de falha do S3\n\n```text\n{b2_root}/checkpoints/s3_failed.json\n```\n\n### Shape mínima\n```json\n{\n  \"event\": \"s3_failed\",\n  \"job_id\": \"job_006_pt_001\",\n  \"sector\": \"s3_visual_planning\",\n  \"failed_at\": \"ISO_TIMESTAMP\",\n  \"status\": \"failed\",\n  \"error\": \"short machine-readable summary\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. Regra do primeiro teste\n\nNo primeiro teste S3-only:\n- `b2_director` inicia S3\n- S3 produz output canónico\n- `b2_director` reconhece `s3_completed`\n- o B2 escreve `b2_completed.json`\n- o bloco pode parar aí\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\content_factory_block2\\\\B2_contracts.md\",\"content\":\"# B2 — Minimal Runtime Contracts (v1)\\n\\n## Objectivo\\n\\nEste documento fecha a camada mínima de contracts operacionais do B2 necessária para ligar o `b2_director` ao S3 no primeiro teste S3-only.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. Bootstrap contract do B2\\n\\n### Contract id\\n- `b2.bootstrap.v1`\\n\\n### Shape mínima\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"kind\\\": \\\"b2_start\\\",\\n  \\\"contract_version\\\": \\\"b2.bootstrap.v1\\\",\\n  \\\"job_id\\\": \\\"job_006_pt_001\\\",\\n  \\\"run_root\\\": \\\"C:/.../run_root\\\",\\n  \\\"b2_root\\\": \\\"C:/.../run_root/b2\\\",\\n  \\\"account_id\\\": \\\"006\\\",\\n  \\\"language\\\": \\\"pt-BR\\\",\\n  \\\"inputs\\\": {\\n    \\\"screenplay_analysis_path\\\": \\\"...\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"mode\\\": \\\"s3_only\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. Resume contract do B2 Director\\n\\n### Contract id\\n- `b2.resume.v1`\\n\\n### Shape mínima\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"kind\\\": \\\"b2_resume\\\",\\n  \\\"contract_version\\\": \\\"b2.resume.v1\\\",\\n  \\\"run_root\\\": \\\"C:/.../run_root\\\",\\n  \\\"b2_root\\\": \\\"C:/.../run_root/b2\\\",\\n  \\\"reason\\\": \\\"s3_completed\\\",\\n  \\\"trigger_artifact\\\": \\\"C:/.../run_root/b2/checkpoints/s3_completed.json\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 3. Checkpoint de request do S3\\n\\nQuando o `b2_director` decide iniciar o S3, ele deve produzir:\\n\\n```text\\n{b2_root}/checkpoints/s3_requested.json\\n```\\n\\n### Shape mínima\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"event\\\": \\\"s3_requested\\\",\\n  \\\"job_id\\\": \\\"job_006_pt_001\\\",\\n  \\\"sector\\\": \\\"s3_visual_planning\\\",\\n  \\\"requested_at\\\": \\\"ISO_TIMESTAMP\\\",\\n  \\\"supervisor_agent_id\\\": \\\"sm_s3_visual_planning\\\",\\n  \\\"mode\\\": \\\"s3_only\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 4. Checkpoint de conclusão do S3\\n\\nQuando o S3 fechar com sucesso utilizável, o supervisor deve produzir:\\n\\n```text\\n{b2_root}/checkpoints/s3_completed.json\\n```\\n\\n### Shape mínima\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"event\\\": \\\"s3_completed\\\",\\n  \\\"job_id\\\": \\\"job_006_pt_001\\\",\\n  \\\"sector\\\": \\\"s3_visual_planning\\\",\\n  \\\"compiled_entities_path\\\": \\\"C:/.../compiled/compiled_entities.json\\\",\\n  \\\"sector_report_path\\\": \\\"C:/.../compiled/s3_sector_report.md\\\",\\n  \\\"completed_at\\\": \\\"ISO_TIMESTAMP\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"completed\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 5. Checkpoint de falha do S3\\n\\n```text\\n{b2_root}/checkpoints/s3_failed.json\\n```\\n\\n### Shape mínima\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"event\\\": \\\"s3_failed\\\",\\n  \\\"job_id\\\": \\\"job_006_pt_001\\\",\\n  \\\"sector\\\": \\\"s3_visual_planning\\\",\\n  \\\"failed_at\\\": \\\"ISO_TIMESTAMP\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"failed\\\",\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"short machine-readable summary\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 6. Regra do primeiro teste\\n\\nNo primeiro teste S3-only:\\n- `b2_director` inicia S3\\n- S3 produz output canónico\\n- `b2_director` reconhece `s3_completed`\\n- o B2 escreve `b2_completed.json`\\n- o bloco pode parar aí\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":838,"output":885,"cacheRead":130816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132539,"cost":{"input":0.002095,"output":0.013275,"cacheRead":0.032704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.048074}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775232131747,"responseId":"resp_0e086492d0456bb30169cfe48598e4819191bc82ed7921f44e"}}
