{"type":"message","id":"3c1c55b3","parentId":"cfbc528e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T18:05:44.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_WdmGxN2BArBZbWy0XeC1opa0|fc_0e086492d0456bb30169d00174e5fc819182e3c8b3674a5430","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Make It Yours\n\nThis is a starting point. Add your own conventions, style, and rules as you figure out what works.\n","newText":"## Make It Yours\n\nThis is a starting point. Add your own conventions, style, and rules as you figure out what works.\n\n## Sector-Specific Lessons (S3)\n\n- Use disk artifacts as truth; agent chat summaries are secondary.\n- Do not regress to ACP for `supervisor -> operator` in this environment.\n- The canonical runtime hop is `exec -> openclaw agent --agent <operator_id> --message ... --json`.\n- Distinguish degraded because of runtime failure from degraded because the test intentionally ran a subset of operators.\n"}]},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\AGENTS.md\",\"edits\":[{\"oldText\":\"## Make It Yours\\n\\nThis is a starting point. Add your own conventions, style, and rules as you figure out what works.\\n\",\"newText\":\"## Make It Yours\\n\\nThis is a starting point. Add your own conventions, style, and rules as you figure out what works.\\n\\n## Sector-Specific Lessons (S3)\\n\\n- Use disk artifacts as truth; agent chat summaries are secondary.\\n- Do not regress to ACP for `supervisor -> operator` in this environment.\\n- The canonical runtime hop is `exec -> openclaw agent --agent <operator_id> --message ... --json`.\\n- Distinguish degraded because of runtime failure from degraded because the test intentionally ran a subset of operators.\\n\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":203,"output":204,"cacheRead":160256,"cacheWrite