o uma unidade �nica.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:72: O Paperclip n�o deve conhecer a topologia interna fina do B2.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:78: Esta pe�a � a ponte entre Paperclip e o interior OpenClaw do Bloco 2.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:87: - devolu��o do estado final do B2 ao Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:98: - bridge com o Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:153: Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:170: 1. **Paperclip activa `w3_block2.py`**\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:189: ### Paperclip espera\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:238: ### Paperclip observa\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:333: 4. devolve o resultado final ao Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:379: ## Como o Paperclip conversa com o B2 sem entender o interior inteiro\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:381: O Paperclip deve conversar apenas com a **boundary surface** do Bloco 2.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:383: ### O que o Paperclip precisa conhecer\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md:409: ### O que o Paperclip n�o precisa conhecer\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.