hitecture.md:90: - a orquestra��o global do Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:93: No caso do S3, o workflow paperclip-facing do sector deve:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:95: 1. receber o payload do Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:101: 7. devolver ao Paperclip o estado final desse trecho\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:107: O Paperclip **n�o invoca os operadores do S3**.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:109: O Paperclip tamb�m **n�o deve, idealmente, invocar directamente a topologia interna do sector**.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:114: Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:115:   -> workflow / mini-orquestrador paperclip-facing do S3\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:126: ### Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:132: ### Workflow paperclip-facing do S3\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:134: - tradu��o do job do Paperclip para o contexto do sector\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:137: - normaliza��o de output do sector para o ecossistema Paperclip\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:158: O workflow paperclip-facing do S3 **n�o � o c�rebro do sector**.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md:173: Ainda sem nome definitivo, o sector poder� ter um entrypoint paperclip-facing como:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\